&lt;li&gt;To redeem the offer, customers need to either call Taj Reservations Worldwide (Need phone number here) OR send an email to&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:reservations@tajhotels.com&quot;&gt;reservations@tajhotels.com&lt;/a&gt;, mentioning Diners Club Worldwide offer.&lt;/li&gt;
